 In this performance you will experience one ordinary day and one maybe a little ordinary life. 

00:01:07.820 --> 00:01:13.080
 The humorous and grotesque parts alternate with the poetics of the drawn black theater, 

00:01:13.080 --> 00:01:17.180
 modern dance numbers alternate with classical ballet 

00:01:17.180 --> 00:01:21.940
 and everything is connected by the actor's pantomime speech of the main actors. 

