 The motto of the new performance is a quote by Albert Einstein. 

00:01:36.800 --> 00:01:44.340
 “I'm afraid of the day when technology development outperforms human relationships. Then the world will have a generation of idiots. ” 

00:01:45.380 --> 00:01:51.040
 The performance is seriously concerned with the contemporary lifestyle. 

00:01:52.600 --> 00:01:56.640
 It shows how modern communication technology drives human destiny. 

